    - _man(6) hau(6) (5)h(a/) (5)k(')(u:) ~~(2)ch(e/)~~ ``ch(e/)(3)``_
        [[man6 hau6 haa5 keoi5 ze3 еХПеАЩеРУдљҐеЧї]]^
        only came to visit him.
